description: The 180 rams were rescued at sea after the Queen Hind cargo ship capsized in November.
title: Queen Hind: 180 rescued sheep arrive at new home in Romania
title_page: Queen Hind: 180 rescued sheep arrive at new home in Romania - BBC News
maintext: "Most of the offers came in without us even doing anything, because people saw the news and got in touch - some just said, 'Hey, I have a farm with some space, if you want I can take some sheep'," she said.
